<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>日本动漫番剧日报｜{{ report.date }}</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-page: #f0ece1;
            --bg-card: rgba(247, 243, 233, 0.92);
            --border-card: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --shadow-card: 0 14px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --text-main: #1a1a1a;
            --text-muted: #5c5c5c;
            --accent: #2d6a4f;
            --accent-2: #3a7d5e;
            --danger: #c0392b;
            --warn: #b8860b;
            --info: #2471a3;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f3e9 0%, #f0ece1 100%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.7;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .wrap { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d6a4f, #3a7d5e);
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 28px 32px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .hero p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: .92;
            color: #f3f9f6;
        }

        .grid { display: grid; gap: 18px; }
        .col-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }

        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
        }

        .card h2, .card h3 {
            margin: 4px 0 12px;
            font-size: 17px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .card h2 { border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 10px; }

        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; }

        th, td {
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding: 10px 12px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            background: rgba(247, 243, 233, 0.95);
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 800;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        tbody tr:nth-child(odd) { background: transparent; }
        tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.035); }
        tbody tr:hover { background: rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.08); }

        .rank {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.1);
            color: #1f5c3f;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; }
        .badge-up { background: #e6f4ec; color: #14532d; }
        .badge-down { background: #fdf0f0; color: #6b1a1a; }
        .badge-flat { background: #f4f4f4; color: #3f3f46; }

        .stars { color: #b8860b; font-weight: 800; }

        .section { margin-top: 10px; }
        .meta { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 13px; }

        .recommend {
            background: rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.08);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .quote {
            background: #fff7d6;
            border-left: 4px solid #b8860b;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 22px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }

        @media (max-width: 860px) { .col-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>📺 日本动漫番剧日报｜{{ report.date }}</h1>
        <p>专业、简洁、高信息密度 · 每日 10 分钟掌握动漫圈核心动态</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>📰 今日动漫圈重要新闻</h2>
            {% for item in report.news %}
            <div style="margin-bottom:18px">
                <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:15px">{{ item.title }}</div>
                <div class="meta">标签：{{ item.tags|join('、') }}</div>
                <div>{{ item.content }}</div>
                <div class="meta">影响分析：{{ item.impact }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🔥 本季新番热度排行榜 TOP10</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr><th>排名</th><th>动画</th><th>类型</th><th>热度</th></tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for row in report.ranking %}
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rank">{{ row.rank }}</span></td>
                    <td><b>{{ row.title }}</b><div class="meta">{{ row.recommend }}</div></td>
                    <td>{{ row.genre }}</td>
                    <td>
                        {% if row.trend == 'up' %}<span class="badge badge-up">↑ {{ row.score }}</span>
                        {% elif row.trend == 'down' %}<span class="badge badge-down">↓ {{ row.score }}</span>
                        {% else %}<span class="badge badge-flat">- {{ row.score }}</span>{% endif %}
                    </td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🎯 今日值得追的番剧</h2>
            {% for item in report.pick %}
            <div class="recommend" style="margin-bottom:14px">
                <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:15px">{{ item.title }}</div>
                <div class="meta">{{ item.status }} · 推荐指数 {{ item.stars }}</div>
                <div>{{ item.highlight }}</div>
                <div class="meta">适合人群：{{ item.audience }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🌱 本周口碑黑马</h2>
            {% for item in report.hit %}
            <div style="margin-bottom:14px">
                <div style="font-weight:700">{{ item.title }} <span class="badge badge-up">逆袭中</span></div>
                <div class="meta">评分变化：{{ item.score_change }}</div>
                <div>{{ item.reason }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🏢 动画制作公司动态</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr><th>公司</th><th>动态类型</th><th>内容</th></tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for row in report.company %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ row.company }}</td>
                    <td>{{ row.type }}</td>
                    <td>{{ row.content }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>📦 销量与商业数据</h2>
            {% if report.sales %}
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr><th>类别</th><th>内容</th><th>趋势</th></tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for row in report.sales %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ row.category }}</td>
                    <td>{{ row.content }}</td>
                    <td>
                        {% if row.trend == 'up' %}<span class="badge badge-up">上升</span>
                        {% elif row.trend == 'down' %}<span class="badge badge-down">下降</span>
                        {% else %}<span class="badge badge-flat">持平</span>{% endif %}
                    </td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
            {% else %}
            <div class="meta">暂无可用数据</div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>📅 未来 30 天值得期待的新番</h2>
            {% for item in report.upcoming %}
            <div style="margin-bottom:14px">
                <div style="font-weight:700">{{ item.title }}</div>
                <div class="meta">{{ item.date }} · {{ item.studio }} · 原作：{{ item.source }}</div>
                <div>{{ item.expectation }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>✨ 今日编辑推荐</h2>
            <div class="recommend">
                <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:15px">{{ report.editor.title }}</div>
                <div class="meta">{{ report.editor.audience }} · 类似作品：{{ report.editor.similar }}</div>
                <div>{{ report.editor.reason }}</div>
            </div>

            <h3 style="margin-top:22px">💬 今日动漫金句</h3>
            <div class="quote">
                <div class="meta">{{ report.quote.source }} · {{ report.quote.character }}</div>
                <div style="font-style:italic; margin:6px 0 10px">“{{ report.quote.line }}”</div>
                <div>{{ report.quote.meaning }}</div>
            </div>

            <h3 style="margin-top:22px">🎬 今日追番清单</h3>
            {% for level, items in report.shortlist.items() %}
            {% set labels = {'5':'★★★★★ 必追','4':'★★★★ 推荐','3':'★★★ 有空可看','2':'★★ 可观望','1':'★ 不推荐'} %}
            {% for title in items %}
            <div class="meta">{{ labels[level] }} —— {{ title }}</div>
            {% endfor %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>📊 Data Source：Nekomini Anime Daily | 📧 Created by：Nekomini Bot | 📅 {{ generated_at }}（北京时间UTC+8）</p>
            <p>power by Nekomini</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
